 131:src/voice.h   **** // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Voice 3: rich power-chord bass with mixed waveforms + huge filter sweep ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
 132:src/voice.h   **** //   Mixed shapes for body: saw root (harmonic-rich), square fifth (hollow), a
