 173:src/voice.h   **** // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Voice 5: screaming aggressive lead ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
 174:src/voice.h   **** //   Detuned sawtooth stack (root + a hair-sharp twin + octave) for a thick,
 175:src/voice.h   **** //   buzzing supersaw bite, pushed up into a cutting register. Heavy drive and a
 176:src/voice.h   **** //   very high filter resonance make the cutoff whistle and scream as pressure
 177:src/voice.h   **** //   sweeps it wide open. Finger-2 pressure piles on ring-mod + wavefold for
