 259:src/voice.h   **** // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Voice 9: kick drum (noise-driven) ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚
 260:src/voice.h   **** //   A deep, punchy thud ‚Äî PLAY IT BY TAPPING. A low sine body with a sub-octave
 261:src/voice.h   **** //   for weight and a quiet octave "click" for beater attack; a whisper of noise
