 570:src/main.cpp  ****             // At zero pressure: cutoff = 0.5x pitch (below fundamental, very dark)
 571:src/main.cpp  ****             // At full pressure: cutoff = 0.5x * 2^(6*prs) ‚Äî exponential opening
 572:src/main.cpp  ****             // 6 octaves of sweep = factor of 64x, so fully open = 32x pitch
 573:src/main.cpp  ****             // This gives the classic Moog "closed ‚Üí wah ‚Üí bright" feel.
 574:src/main.cpp  ****             // Power-3 on pressure so the bottom half stays dark and controlled.
 575:src/main.cpp  ****             // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Smootherstep pressure curves (6x‚Åµ - 15x‚Å¥ + 10x¬≥) ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î
